catList: Overview of machine tools, CNC, cutting tools, and CAD/CAM; analytical methods in manufacturing processes; analysis of force, power, stress, temperature , vibrations etc. in manufacturing processes; recent and future trends in manufacturing processes: high speed machining, sensor-assisted and unattended manufacturing; case studies from tool and die, automotive and aerospace  industries.Lab: NC programming demonstration;  force, vibration etc. measurements on machine tools.
